value.name: Murderer 🕹️ Play Murderer on CrazyGames
value.snippet: Murderer is a first-person detective multiplayer game that is inspired by games like Among Us and Werewolf. There are three roles, murderer, gunner, and civilian. The murderer has a knife and must kill all civilians, the gunner has a revolver and must kill the murderer, and civilians can find three clues and get a revolver.

You must move around and explore the vast 3D city and try to bring the criminals and gangsters to justice.

deepLinks.name: Shell Shockers
deepLinks.snippet: Shell Shockers (Shellshock.io) is a multiplayer .io FPS game featuring eggs armed with guns. You control one of these weapon-wielding eggs in one of four online game modes where the aim is to shatter your opponents with bullets and bombs. It&#39;s the ultimate online egg shooting game!

deepLinks.name: Merc Zone
deepLinks.snippet: Merc Zone is an online multiplayer FPS game made by Blue Wizard Digital. Find your favorite weapon and fight in various game modes and maps. This stylish suit-and-tie shooter features fast-paced action and a sleek 3D aesthetic that makes you want to play more!
